<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you don’t want to do all these steps, it is a great idea to get a portable air filter. </span><a href="https://dankstop.com/collections/smokebuddy" target="_blank" title="Smokebuddy" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Smokebuddy</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> has been around for over a decade, protecting smokers from any unwanted scents before they linger. They come in multiple sizes and colors and can last upwards of 600+ uses! Simply remove the caps and exhale through the mouthpiece as the Smokebuddy eliminates odor and removes smoke. This nifty invention is a great help to any smoker no matter the situation, hence why it made </span><a href="https://dankstop.com/blogs/wiki/5-bong-accessories-you-didn-t-know-you-needed" target="_blank" title="Smoking Accessories Every Smoker Needs" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span style="font-weight: 400;">one of our lists for needed accessories</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.<br><br><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1085/8818/files/4_d2674cf4-fd8e-40f1-a80a-ca9557b24190.png?v=1533911836" alt="smokebuddy"><br></span></p>
