<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Some people swear by smoking in their hotel bathrooms because of the added layer of discretion added by an extra door. Turning on the air vent during your session and blowing into it should help dissipate the smell. Be sure to spray some air freshener around after you’re done, since most hotel bathrooms don’t have any windows to help air the place out. If you find air fresheners too potent, </span><a href="https://dankstop.com/products/bluntmax-premium-incense-single-pack" target="_blank" title="Incense Sticks" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span style="font-weight: 400;">try out some incense sticks</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> for a more calming, natural aroma. </span><a href="https://dankstop.com/collections/bluntmax" target="_blank" title="Bluntmax" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bluntmax</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> offers plenty of scents, as well as larger quantities.</span></p>
